column9:
It's fast. At the heart of the Wyse Z90 lies an engine, where all the major system elements - 

CPU cores, vector engines, and a unified video decoder for HD decoding tasks - live on the same piece of 

silicon. This design concept eliminates one of the fundamental constraints that limit performance. Whether 

you want the best 2D or 3D graphics, HD video, or the ability to embed custom Windows applications that 

execute right on the Z90, you'll have power to spare.
